      "content": "Hey, I'm looking over the Q3 route efficiency reports. We've had a bunch of complaints from the driver unions about how certain routes are being assigned, specifically regarding the demographic breakdown of the drivers getting the longer, more difficult hauls. Can you explain the logic behind these specific assignments? I need to justify these patterns before the board meeting.",
